column2:
"<%me>.
I'm glad you're doing fine.
Do you need anything?"
"You want information about when my sister went missing 10 years ago?"

"I can only vaguely remember being in a city.
Then Dark Falz appeared...
Then, Mr. Gettemhart and sister..."

"…...Ngh.
I'm sorry. I need some time to calm down."

"What does the Dark Falz look like?
...That's a strange question."

"I can't remember clearly,
but if I'm not mistaken..."

"Y-yeah.
It was definitely not an adult woman, at least."
